14-45a096b7535e","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"75e1cbe2-5fc2-4fd4-b4bb-159a431206ad","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","text":"Florenc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false}],"blockProperties":[{"id":"18ad5a9b-2e30-44b5-8855-cf81596b76a0","type":"block/alignment/right","metadata":{},"isDeleted":false}],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"14fac777-7e66-4996-b868-235110493a78","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[],"children":[],"metadata":{},"relation":{}},{"id":"6bdb0445-7cb8-49c3-a730-41ba18ce6670","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Buonarroto, — I received the bread; it is good, but it is not good enough to invest in as there would be little profit. I gave the messenger five carlini, but he would hardly hand the bread over. From thy last letter I learn that Lorenzo [Strozzi] will pass this way and that thou wishest me to entertain him. Evidently thou hast little understanding of how I am placed here. However, I hold thee excused. What I can do I will. I hear that Gismondo is coming here to arrange his affairs. Tell him from me that he is not to expect any help from me, not because I do not love him as a brother, but because I am unable to help him in any way. I am compelled to love myself more than others, and I cannot supply all my own needs. I live here surrounded hy the greatest anxieties, suffering the greatest bodily fatigues: I have not a friend of any sort, and do not want one; I have not so much time as suffices for me to eat the necessary food. However, I trust I may have no additional worries, for I could not bear another ounce. My advice about the shop is that ye should strive to do your best; and I am glad that Giovansimone has begun to do well. Endeavour by just means to increase what ye already have, or at least to preserve it, so that ye may know how to deal with larger matters later on; for I am hoping that when I come back ye will be able to set up for yourselves, if ye be men enough. Tell Lodovico that I have not answered him because I have not had time, and do not be surprised when I fail to write.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b7a7b62d-41c7-48a9-9e7c-4d0ca9e6fe28","type":"salutation","start":0,"end":9,"value":"","text":"Buonarrot","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"4eec135b-a162-42c5-ac72-1767c4293aac","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":9,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"Buonarrot","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"5844ed90-6c1c-400a-b797-1ee0dde4b419","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":14,"end":14,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"c25a556e-2056-456a-80ec-2db443e12454","type":"codex/meta-relation-reference","start":16,"end":23,"value":"6daba98a-e99d-45bb-8b27-894df1156aa9","text":"receive","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"463b4e3d-6f80-47c3-94d8-b378e938b14d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":29,"end":33,"value":"e85fcd5f-8308-45df-bac6-b33328fc0322","text":"brea","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"8099130f-1182-4a41-bc94-e74aa5fd18ad","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":120,"end":120,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"cb5f8cab-ec85-45b1-bf63-2ab18e50e63b","type":"style/italics","start":146,"end":152,"value":"","text":"carlin","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"f7b6b1d5-c54d-40a7-9327-c18150f368f4","type":"language","start":146,"end":152,"value":"it","text":"carlin","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"42f82919-23d6-4080-b8b1-c3ff83bca491","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":201,"end":203,"value":"eb5c2755-f869-4ca7-8733-1c39b95bc7a0","text":"th","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":